00158         private ArrayList<LatLng> decodePoly(String encoded) {
00159                 ArrayList<LatLng> poly = new ArrayList<LatLng>();
00160                 int index = 0, len = encoded.length();
00161                 int lat = 0, lng = 0;
00162                 while (index < len) {
00163                         int b, shift = 0, result = 0;
00164                         do {
00165                                 b = encoded.charAt(index++) - 63;
00166                                 result |= (b & 0x1f) << shift;
00167                                 shift += 5;
00168                         } while (b >= 0x20);
00169                         int dlat = ((result & 1) != 0 ? ~(result >> 1) : (result >> 1));
00170                         lat += dlat;
00171                         shift = 0;
00172                         result = 0;
00173                         do {
00174                                 b = encoded.charAt(index++) - 63;
00175                                 result |= (b & 0x1f) << shift;
00176                                 shift += 5;
00177                         } while (b >= 0x20);
00178                         int dlng = ((result & 1) != 0 ? ~(result >> 1) : (result >> 1));
00179                         lng += dlng;
00180 
00181                         LatLng position = new LatLng((double) lat / 1E5, (double) lng / 1E5);
00182                         poly.add(position);
